    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional example of automotive engineering, presenting in showroom condition. The heart of this machine is a high-revving, naturally aspirated engine featuring variable valve timing and forged internals, delivering a seamless power band. The longitudinal drivetrain is paired with a precise short-throw manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. The suspension architecture\u2014utilizing MacPherson struts up front and a sophisticated multi-link rear\u2014has been preserved with OEM-spec bushings to ensure razor-sharp turn-in. Aerodynamic integrity is maintained with original body panels and factory-correct tolerances. Every fluid has been analyzed, and the undercarriage remains free of oxidation or thermal fatigue. This is a collector-grade vehicle for the enthusiast who prioritizes mechanical purity and uncompromising performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
